<plot>This documentary - Verhaal van Verlangen - shows how the Polish family of Lech is waiting and longing for his return from the Netherlands. He is working there to earn money for his family, who are living in poverty. We see his family members desperate for his return, hoping that he will make their lives better.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?638249</url></doc>
